<!DOCTYPE suite SYSTEM "https://testng.org/testng-1.0.dtd" >
<suite name="Suite1" verbose="1">
    <test name="Smoke Test 1">
        <packages>
            <package name="myapp.tests.smoketest" />
            <package name="myapp.tests.smoketest.excelatautomation" />
        </packages>
    </test>
</suite>
<!--
1. xml files are used to run test classes
2. suite > test > package > groups > class > method
3. verbose: the amount of info you see on the console
4. Save the xml file before you run (command-S or File -> Save All)
5. If path is not correct then we see No tests were found error message
-->